text: Ic seah in healle hring <gyldenne> men sceawian, modum gleawe, ferþþum frode.
<Friþospede> bæd god nergende gæste sinum se þe wende wriþan; word æfter cwæð hring on hyrede, hælend nemde tillfremmendra.
Him torhte in gemynd his dryhtnes naman dumba brohte ond in eagna gesihð, gif þæs æþelan goldes tacen ongietan cuþe <ond> <dryhtnes> dolg, don swa þæs beages benne cwædon.
Ne mæg þære bene æniges monnes <ungefullodre> godes ealdorburg gæst gesecan, rodera ceastre.
Ræde, se þe wille, hu ðæs wrætlican wunda cwæden hringes to hæleþum, þa he in healle wæs wylted ond wended wloncra folmum.
